item.title: school
item.description: (transcribed from Book Six 4:48pm JST Friday 26 June 2009 (day 14338)) 3:05AM Wednesday 24 November 1993 (Day 61) "Today" Maggie & I took her car to Goodson Pontiac for a check up. My car started making a thumping sound on the way to school. Marcel was not in graphics. Neither was my chair. I grabbed one from a nearby classroom. I was spotted by Christine T so I talked to her for a while.
